The mesh object folders in this directory (milk/, porcelain_mug/,
wine_bottle/) are vendored from the LIBERO benchmark
(https://github.com/Lifelong-Robot-Learning/LIBERO), originally under
libero/libero/assets/{stable_hope_objects,turbosquid_objects}. They are
self-contained robosuite object XMLs (mesh + texture paths relative to each
XML) and are redistributed here under LIBERO's MIT license, reproduced below,
so OdorSim does not need a LIBERO checkout.

